OL,3,CNorthern Ireland police allegedly
OL,4,Cspied on BBC journalist
OL,6,FClaims have emerged that a former BBC
OL,7,Fjournalist was spied on by police
OL,8,Fwhile he was working on a documentary
OL,9,Fthat scrutinised the independence of
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland's police watchdog in
OL,11,F2011.
OL,13,FThe BBC has now instructed lawyers to
OL,14,Fcontact a specialist tribunal over the
OL,15,Fallegations that surveillance was
OL,16,Fcarried out on former employee Vincent
OL,17,FKearney.
OL,19,FMr Kearney, who is the current
OL,20,FNorthern Editor at RTE, said he is
OL,21,Fdetermined to find out what happened.
