OL,3,CNorthern Ireland police allegedly
OL,4,Cspied on BBC journalist
OL,6,FThe claims emerged as part of a case
OL,7,Falready being examined by the
OL,8,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal (IPT)
OL,9,Finto allegations two other
OL,10,Finvestigative reporters working in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland have been subject to
OL,12,Funlawful covert surveillance by police.
OL,14,FIn 2018, Barry McCaffrey and Trevor
OL,15,FBirney were controversially arrested
OL,16,Fas part of a police investigation into
OL,17,Fthe alleged leaking of a confidential
OL,18,Fdocument that appeared in a
OL,19,Fdocumentary they made on a Troubles
OL,20,Fmassacre.
