OL,3,CNorthern Ireland police allegedly
OL,4,Cspied on BBC journalist
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,Flater unreservedly apologised for how
OL,8,Fthe men had been treated and agreed to
OL,9,Fpay #875,000 in damages to the
OL,10,Fjournalists and the film company
OL,11,Fbehind the documentary.
OL,13,FIn 2019, Mr Birney and Mr McCaffrey
OL,14,Flodged a complaint with the IPT asking
OL,15,Fit to establish whether there had been
OL,16,Fany unlawful surveillance of them.
