OL,3,CNorthern Ireland police allegedly
OL,4,Cspied on BBC journalist
OL,6,FThe tribunal is also probing two other
OL,7,Finstances of police surveillance
OL,8,Fagainst Mr McCaffrey in 2013 and 2011.
OL,9,FIt sat for a brief hearing in February
OL,10,Fand is due to resume its work later in
OL,11,Fthe year.
OL,13,FIt is understood information
OL,14,Fsuggesting Mr Kearney might also have
OL,15,Fbeen subject to surveillance emerged
OL,16,Fduring the disclosure processes
OL,17,Frelated to Mr McCaffrey and Mr
OL,18,FBirney's case.
