OL,4,Cspied on BBC journalist
OL,6,FA BBC spokesperson said: "We have
OL,7,Finstructed lawyers to write to the
OL,8,FInvestigatory Powers Tribunal about
OL,9,Fthe alleged PSNI surveillance of
OL,10,Ftelephone data linked to the work of
OL,11,FVincent Kearney during his employment
OL,12,Fwith the BBC, in connection with a BBC
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Spotlight programme
OL,14,Fbroadcast in 2011.
OL,16,F"We think that serious issues of
OL,17,Fpublic interest are involved,
OL,18,Fincluding in relation to the adverse
OL,19,Feffects that surveillance may have on
OL,20,Fjournalistic investigations and
OL,21,Ffreedoms."
