OL,3,CNorthern Ireland police allegedly
OL,4,Cspied on BBC journalist
OL,6,FThe 2011 Spotlight programme examined
OL,7,Fallegations that the independence of
OL,8,Fthe office of the Police Ombudsman had
OL,9,Fbeen compromised and that it was not
OL,10,Finvestigating complaints about police
OL,11,Fmisconduct, including allegations of
OL,12,Fcollusion, with sufficient rigour.
OL,14,FOmbudsman Al Hutchinson rejected
OL,15,Fclaims his investigations lacked
OL,16,Findependence. He resigned in January
OL,17,F2012.
